<h2>By region</h2>
<p>Using <a href="https://www.hesa.ac.uk/data-and-analysis/sb268/figure-16">Higher Education Graduate Outcomes Statistics</a> we can look at how well different regions and nations of the UK retain their graduates after education. We calculate the percentage of graduates who remain in the same region/nation for work as the region/nation of their higher education provider.</p>

